OL,3,CHarry Redknapp in upbeat mood - as he
OL,4,Cdreams of Gold Cup glory
OL,6,FHarry Redknapp was in an upbeat mood
OL,7,Fas he arrived at Cheltenham this
OL,8,Fafternoon - hoping this will be the
OL,9,Fday he realises his dream of seeing
OL,10,Fone of his horses ride to glory in The
OL,11,FGold Cup.
OL,13,FThe former Spurs manager is the owner
OL,14,Fof The Jukebox Man, which is currently
OL,15,Fjoint favourite for the showpiece race
OL,16,Fat Prestbury Park, and is trained
OL,17,Fnearby at the Naunton Downs Estate in
OL,18,Fthe Cotswolds.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
