OL,3,CHarry Redknapp in upbeat mood - as he
OL,4,Cdreams of Gold Cup glory
OL,6,FA sell-out crowd of 66,000 will watch
OL,7,Fone of the biggest days in the horse-
OL,8,Fracing calendar, with all eyes on the
OL,9,Fbig race at 4pm.
OL,11,FHarry, who won the FA Cup with
OL,12,FPortsmouth in 2008 and was crowned
OL,13,FKing of the Jungle in 2018, arrived at
OL,14,Fthe racecourse with his wife Sandra,
OL,15,Fand said he'd slept well.
OL,17,FHe said: "It is the World Cup final of
OL,18,FNational Hunt racing and I'm looking
OL,19,Fforward to it. We'll do our best -
OL,20,Fhe's got a chance."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
