OL,3,CHarry Redknapp in upbeat mood - as he
OL,4,Cdreams of Gold Cup glory
OL,6,FA host of celebrities arrived at
OL,7,FPrestbury Park this morning, including
OL,8,FTommy Fury, actor Hero Fiennes and TV
OL,9,Fpresenter Nick Knowles.
OL,11,FNick Knowles said: "This is one of the
OL,12,Fgreat sporting events. It is the start
OL,13,Fof the sporting calendar - the world
OL,14,Fis waking up after the dark winter -
OL,15,Fand it is this (Cheltenham) and the
OL,16,FSix Nations that gets everything
OL,17,Fstarted for the sporting year."
OL,19,FTommy Fury, Nick Knowles and actor
OL,20,FHero Fiennes look ahead to the big day
OL,21,Fat Cheltenham
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
