OL,3,CHarry Redknapp in upbeat mood - as he
OL,4,Cdreams of Gold Cup glory
OL,6,FGold Cup day is seen by many as the
OL,7,Fbiggest day in the National Hunt
OL,8,Fcalendar, and attracts racing fans
OL,9,Ffrom all over the country
OL,11,FOne of the youngest fans at the track
OL,12,Ftoday, was Oscar Price, who was
OL,13,Fproudly sitting on the shoulders of
OL,14,Fdad Andrew.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
