OL,3,CHarry Redknapp in upbeat mood - as he
OL,4,Cdreams of Gold Cup glory
OL,6,FAndrew said: "He loves it here. He's
OL,7,Fbeen racing since he was a young
OL,8,Fchild. We're big followers of the
OL,9,Fsport and have some friends racing
OL,10,Fhere today. We've been here for three
OL,11,Fdays this week and had a really nice
OL,12,Ftime."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
